<plot>Mr Watson is an overweight middle-aged man. He lives a life that is repetitive and systematically self-pleasing. He visits his local video shop to rent a video like he does every other day. On this occasion he has difficulty on finding a film that he hasn't seen before, so he asks the video shop owner for some help. The Video shop owner offers Mr Watson a film that that will change his life forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?599015</url></doc>
